snippet.title: Wayfinder: Summer Game Fest Trailer | Early Access Coming this Summer
snippet.description:
►► Wishlist on PlayStation Today: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10002172 
►► Wishlist on Steam Today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1171690/Wayfinder/

The world of Evenor needs champions! ⚔️

Heroes reborn, become a #Wayfinder and protect this world and its inhabitants from the corruption of the Gloom.

Enjoy this latest look into @playwayfinder and prepare to stand together to #ControltheChaos! 
Learn more about Wayfinder and Wishlist today!

#Wayfinder #SummerGameFest
